PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Supply and Services of ROBERT MURRAY McCLELLAND, of Downsview, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Post Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years, in the place of Lawrence S.
